<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>٢ في <span class="c1">"ط"</span>: <span class="c1">"و"</span>.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>